channel.title: Cant find the portforward guide for my router
channel.description:
Im using Speedtouch585. Ive searched for a portforwardingguide to Runescape but there is no? If you know a game that you port forward in the same way or if you have the time to give me a directed link to the guide I would be greatful.
Have I been searching for the wrong guide? I cant start my private server anyway.

item.title: Cant find the portforward guide for my router
item.dc:creator: @adu adu
item.description:
@adu wrote:

Go start>run>cmd

Type ‘ipconfig’ and look at the ip that is 192.168..**

Now goto your router and forward the port you want using the 192.168..** ip.
